Classes

class  FdoIChangeLongTransactionSet
 The FdoIChangeLongTransactionSet interface defines the ChangeLongTransactionSet command, which allows the user to add a transaction to, remove a transaction from, or clear the long transaction selection set. Users can add or remove long transactions to the selection set for which they have access privileges. Any attempt to add a long transaction for which the user does not have the access privilege will result in a failure of the command. More...
